In this PR, we decompose the differential on a homological complex of the form `mapBifunctor (mapBifunctor K‚ÇÅ K‚ÇÇ F‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ c‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ) K‚ÇÉ G c‚ÇÑ` into three components.
